# Office + home dev sync

## Canonical clone

| Machine | Path |
|---------|------|
| macOS (both) | `~/dev/TMMT` |
| App workspace | `~/dev/TMMT/tmmt-os` |

Legacy `~/Desktop/AIX_Command_Center/TMMT MANAGEMENT` — migrate off; do not treat as source of truth.

## Git branch

- **Production / shared default:** `main`
- Active feature work: short-lived branches → PR → `main`
- Retire long-lived `cursor/tmmt-management-initial-setup` after merge

## Sync scripts (repo)

- `ops/dev-machine/bootstrap-macos.sh` — first clone + Node 20 + `npm ci`
- `ops/dev-machine/sync-machine.sh` — `git pull` (cron-safe)
- `ops/dev-machine/install-launchd.sh` — office auto-pull every 15 min

`SYNC_MODE=code` (default): pull only.  
`SYNC_MODE=dev`: pull + `npm ci` in `tmmt-os/`.

## Secrets

- `tmmt-os/.env.local` per machine; copy manually; never commit.
